Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:47.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一份诺玛早餐.\N特制的.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of Norma's breakfasts.\NMade special.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝保佑诺玛.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God bless Norma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:56.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,先放着吧. 先放着吧, 谢了.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe later. Maybe later, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:01.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,局里的事务怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's things at the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:04.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,厄尔的棋局\N是最伤脑筋的.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earle's chess game\Nis the big concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:07.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人毫无松懈\N的意思.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man has a poor sense\Nof recreation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:09.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:12.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正挺着呢, 暂时还行.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're holding up, for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:18.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿, 你和库珀能处理好的.\N这个镇单纯的很.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you and Cooper can handle it.\Nlt's a pretty simple town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:22.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,以前是.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:29.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想世界正\N赶着我们前进呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess the world's\Njust caught up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安妮.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:59.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨.\N- 嗨.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hi.\N- Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:03.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉, 这是我妹妹, 安妮.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly, this is my sister, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:07.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨, 安妮. 欢迎.\N诺玛和我讲过你所有的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Annie. Welcome.\NNorma's told me all about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:12.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我所有的事?\N- 雪莉就像自家人一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- All about me?\N- Shelly's like family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:16.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的家, 没有一个\N像样的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With our family, that's not exactly\Na character reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:19.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你和妈妈相处的如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you and Mom get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:22.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 我们可以谈谈她,\N又或者谈点别的，能让我们高兴的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can talk about her,\Nor we can feel good about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:24.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我选后者.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l vote for plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:28.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是. 我很高兴你来这.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too. l'm glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:30.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点奇怪. 现实世界.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels a little strange. The real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一些琐事, 比如我差点忘了\N怎么用钱.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little things, like l'd almost forgotten\Nhow to use money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:37.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,最近我们修道院里\N用的都是代币.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Closest we get in the convent\Nwas bingo chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:41.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不用优待我, 诺玛. 你保证.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No charity, Norma. Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:45.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心,\N我会让你工作到倒下为止.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry,\Nl'm gonna work you till you drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:51.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,引人注目.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:15.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里快崩溃了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry's about to hit bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:18.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他吃东西吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls he eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:24.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得他什么时候\N会回来工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When do you think\Nhe'll come back to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:26.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们很快就会知道的.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess we'll find out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:28.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,需要帮忙吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Need a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题\N应该由我来问你.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a question\Nl should be asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是高级督察, 库珀.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the senior lawman, Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:36.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是\N各安其位吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just let the rain fall\Nas it has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:39.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再说, 我讨厌文书工作.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, l hate paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:43.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿比调查局那边还乱,\N全都是些国际档案.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is worse than the Bureau,\Nwith all its international documentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:46.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,埃卡, 乔西...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eckhardt, Josie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:49.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是她的验尸报告.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the autopsy on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:52.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,海沃德医生说\N他无法确定死因.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doc Hayward said\Nhe couldn't determine cause of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:55.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尸体只有65磅.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The body only weighed 65 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:59.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那怎么可能?\N- 我不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- How is that possible?\N- l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:02.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或许和她死去时\N我在房间里所见的有关.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe something to do with\Nwhat l saw in the room when she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:06.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或许在我们路过坟墓是\N最好要吹着口哨.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we'd better just whistle\Non our way past the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 就是.\N- 厄尔那边呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah.\N- Anything on Earle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:16.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,踪迹全消.\N还在等他回应呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trail's stone-cold.\NStill waiting for his response.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 鞋.\N- 是拖鞋.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Slip.\N- Slippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:40.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗, 里欧,\N一个人是不懂欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Leo,\Nyou can't really appreciate
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:47.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乡村生活有多么的滋补\N除非你真正身在其中生活.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how tonic country life is\Nuntil you're actually right here, living it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:51.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 烟斗?\N- 好极了.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Pipe?\N- Splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:55.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,即便你之前\N去过乡村,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you've been\Nto the country before,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:59.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当你试图去想像时\N却像回到过去,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:07:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you try to imagine\Nwhat it would be like to go back,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:02.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,影像是残缺不全的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the image is imperfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:07.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,脑袋的影像\N总是不完美的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mental image\Nis always imperfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:09.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我说的对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am l right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:13.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,心照不宣是可以接受的, 里欧.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tacit agreement is acceptable, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:18.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你此时无声胜有声.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your silence speaks volumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:24.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,又或者说, 至少是一段\N偶然未加标点的文章段落.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or if not volumes, at least the\Noccasional unpunctuated paragraph.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:32.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好, 让我们来看看可怜的库珀\N这次是怎么走出这一步棋.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see what move our poor\NCooper's come up with this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:49.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是一步棋.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:52.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个把戏.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:56.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他让这游戏陷入了僵局.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's playing a stalemate game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:08:02.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀根本不知道\N有僵局这一招!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooper doesn't know\Nthe meaning of stalemate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:06.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在帮他.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:16.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能容忍别人\N不按规矩玩游戏.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l cannot tolerate people\Nwho do not play by the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:20.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那些不安本分的人!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who shirk the standards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:29.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很多人会因此而后悔的.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many people are going to regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:07.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,会了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:13.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,女士们, 容许我说,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies, may l say,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:19.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩将如此愉悦的代表着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll both delightfully represent
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:23.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,神圣的大自然.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the sanctity of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:25.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来根烟?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:29.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我宁愿让肺保持干净.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l prefer to keep my chest clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:33.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,伟大的神, 真健康.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great god, fitness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:38.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你和品寇谈过了吗?\N- 品寇是什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Have you spoken with Pinkle?\N- What's a Pinkle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:41.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他是来为松鼬\N演讲的.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's giving a talk\Non the pine-weasel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:44.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 濒临绝种动物.\N- 哦, 有意思.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- The endangered animal.\N- Oh, lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:46.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么来的? 是浣熊吗? 还是别的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? A raccoon or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:48.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是一种鼬.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ferret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:50.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:52.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 好极了.\N你们俩该协力合作.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, great.\NYou two should coordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:54.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你想的美.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:02.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看来你\N很卖力啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're trying\Nto run lumber upstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么可以帮你吗, 维乐先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can l help you, Mr. Wheeler?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,荷恩. 嗯, 就是我们\N那天晚餐时说的.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horne. Well, the talk\Nthat we had at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不能--\N- 很抱歉我当时的无礼, 你也觉得吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l can't--\N- l'm sorry l was rude, wasn't l?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:13.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只是每当提到我家里,\N我就会有点激动.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just that when it comes to my family,\Nl get a little excitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:15.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是我的错，我又不是谁，却在这儿到处指手划脚的\N- 我们需要帮助, 人尽皆知,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who am l to waltz in out of nowhere?\N- We need help, anyone can see that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:19.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我想不出有谁\N比你更胜任这工作了.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and l can't think of anyone\Nbetter qualified for the job than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,喂?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:25.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们到底在讲什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we talking about anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在道歉\N同时你也道歉.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was apologizing\Nand you were apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:30.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩都有不是了.\N你想出去走走吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both real sorry about something.\NYou wanna go out somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:33.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不合时宜, 对吧? 不太好?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad time, right? lt's not good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 不, 不, 很合时宜.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, no, it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:37.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去野餐怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a picnic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:42.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要些户外用品.\N篮子, 地毯...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need outdoors stuff.\NA basket, blanket...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:44.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,食物.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会煮东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know how to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我敢打赌\N有人帮你在厨房里做呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll bet you someone\Nin the kitchen does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:53.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是让人们知道\N松鼬到底长什么样子.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just to show people\Nwhat the pine-weasel looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:55.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全能理解这个概念,\N饼扣先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l understand the concept perfectly,\NMr. Dinkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:57.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是品扣. 我名字叫品扣.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pinkle. The name is Pinkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:11:00.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我先讲清楚\N用一个动物标本
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:11:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what l'm trying to make clear\Nis that using a stuffed animal
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:04.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去象征濒临绝种的动物\N作为一个生态倡议书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to represent an endangered species\Nas an ecological protest
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:08.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,构建极端不和谐啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,constitutes the supreme incongruity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:12.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 说的是, 基巴.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's clear, Dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:17.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:20.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿, 库.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:23.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在国际刑警组织那儿\N拿到了乔西的档案.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got Josie's dossier\Nin from lnterpol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:26.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没兴趣.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:29.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,另外，杀死埃卡,\N还有试图谋杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln addition to killing Eckhardt,\Ntrying to kill me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:31.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 和在西雅图杀死乔纳森,\N- 都结案了.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- and killing Jonathan in Seattle,\N- Closed cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她还因多宗重案\N在香港被通缉.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's also wanted for a variety\Nof felonies in Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要听这些.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't need to hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:38.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她还因卖淫\N被逮捕过2次, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's also had\Ntwo prostitution arrests, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:55.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 最终这些会帮助你了解\N她其实是个不知悔改的惯犯.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, eventually it's gonna help you\Nto know she was a hardened criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:57.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个杀手.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:01.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,走开.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:03.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道现在不易过.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know it's not easy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:05.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,走开行不行.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:11.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,滚开! 滚!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,门是开着的.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:37.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乡村习俗. 我们都互相信任.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A country habit. We're all so trusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:40.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫琼斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:43.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是埃卡先生生前的\N行政助理.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was executive assistant\Nto the late Mr. Eckhardt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:49.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:03.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是来加紧处理\N他尸体运回香港的.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've come to expedite the transport\Nof his body back to Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:10.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,悲剧啊, 发生那些事.\N你知道的, 他真的爱乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tragic, what happened.\NYou know, he really did love Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,难道我们不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:16.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们将被埋葬\N在一起.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to be buried\Nside by side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:20.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么他们就可以\N互相监视了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they can keep an eye\Non each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:23.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你的挖苦\N是有因由的.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess you have your reasons\Nto be bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:27.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 尽管把我称作一个健康的无神论者吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just call me a healthy skeptic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:31.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 说你来见我的真正\N目的是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, why did you really\Ncome to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:37.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我来这儿给你捎个礼物.\N可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l came here to give you a gift.\NMay l?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:39.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不这么想.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:48.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,慢点.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:04.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,托马斯送的.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:08.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有些东西要整理,\N然后，我今晚就走.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have a few things to tidy up,\Nthen l'll be leaving tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:12.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你走运, 马爹利太太.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Mrs. Martell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:32.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了, 我找\N比尔或艾琳·海沃德.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, l'm looking\Nfor Bill or Eileen Hayward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:35.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 他们现在不在家呢.\N能帮你吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they're not here right now.\NCan l help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:37.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧, 杰尔·奎格医生,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l'm Dr. Gerald Craig,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:40.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是伟在医校的\N老朋友.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an old friend of Will's\Nfrom medical school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:43.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 那, 你看,\N我去斯波坎市参加会议
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, well, you see,\Nl have a convention in Spokane
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:48.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就想顺道拜访\N给他们个惊喜.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and so l just thought l'd swing by\Nand surprise them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:50.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪个女儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which daughter are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:53.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 唐娜.\N- 唐娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Donna.\N- Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:56.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你要进来坐坐吗,\N奎格医生?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come in,\NDr. Craig?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:59.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那就打搅了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:15:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'd appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:17.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要给你拿点喝的吗,\N奎格医生? 汽水之类的?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can l get you something to drink,\NDr. Craig? A pop or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:20.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你, 不了, 不了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:23.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们当地的报纸?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls this your local paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.43,0:15:25.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊. 相当小的镇, 呵?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Pretty small town, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:28.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这, 在你住进城市之前\N可别瞧不起这儿镇小.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, don't knock small towns\Nuntil you've lived in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:30.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜, 知道吗,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:36.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看来伟已经在这儿\N找到他自己一片小小的宁静乐土了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems like Will has found himself\Na little piece of heaven here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:42.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 你不还有2个姐妹吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, don't you have two sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:46.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是啊, 他们比我小.\N- 2个都和你一样漂亮?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah, they're younger than me.\N- Are they both as beautiful as you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:49.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 我不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:56.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗, 你爸爸和我,\N我们以前常围坐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, your dad and l,\Nwe used to sit around
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:16:00.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,试着去设想\N我们未来的生活会怎样.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:16:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and try to figure\Nhow our lives would work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:06.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在看来，他似乎\N比我更接近目标.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems like he's come\Na little closer to the mark than l have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:10.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在读高中?\N- 是啊，真不幸.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're in high school?\N- Unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:13.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得是.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l felt exactly the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:16.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你了解, 高中难熬啊,\N是啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, high school is difficult,\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:18.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道\N你将来想要干什么,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea\Nwhat you want to do with your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:22.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎你的人生\N一片茫然.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it seems that absolutely none of it\Napplies to your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:24.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:27.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 别担心. 会好起来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't worry. lt'll all work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:32.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,目前来说, 你就只管去做些荒谬言行\N尽情享受所有的怪诞事物好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, you just enjoy it\Nin all its absurdity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:34.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:38.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 我带了个小礼物给你爸爸.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, l have a small gift for your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:43.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么, 我能相信你不会打开它吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, can l trust you not to open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:45.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:48.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吧, 提到学校,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, speaking of school,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:52.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,伟和我就是30年前\N的这个月毕业的.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will and l graduated\N30 years ago this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:56.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我--\N一个给他的小纪念品.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So l--\Nlt's a small remembrance for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 我该走了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l should be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:03.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 这是我住的地方\N的电话号码.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is the number\Nwhere l'm staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:08.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,希望迟点再会, 唐娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope to see you later, Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:10.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:52.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你准备的怎样了, 皮特?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you holding up, Pete?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:58.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经查过历史纪录里的\N每一个比赛的僵局了.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been through every\Nstalemate game in recorded history.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:03.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还草草的编了几个\N农家风格的僵局
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l've jerry-rigged\Na few of these country standoffs
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,书上没有的.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they don't write about in books.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:10.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不过没用. 我意思是,\N这世上根本就没有僵局
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's no use. l mean,\Nthere isn't a stalemate game on earth
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:14.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你连几个步兵\N都没损失.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you don't lose\Nat least a few foot soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:16.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是指, 就连最经典的和斯曼棋局.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean, the classic Herbstman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:21.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你也只能救6步棋.\N目前, 我能作点改善.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wind up with six pieces.\NNow, l can improve on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:26.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但就算我在一半时间内走到那儿\N救12步,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if l get there in half the time\Nand wind up with 1 2,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:31.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那意味着还是有6个人会死.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that means six people die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你尽力而为吧, 皮特.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, Pete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:39.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,云顿·厄尔有性急的恶习\N和他的天才一样是与生俱来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Windom Earle's genius carries with it\Nthe vice of impatience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:43.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他不想要兵卒.\N他要皇.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't want pawns.\NHe wants royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:47.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,保护那些, 特别是皇后,\N那么我们就能挫败他.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect those, particularly the queen,\Nand we can frustrate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:49.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能那样走.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.95,0:18:52.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的学生们.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My students.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:57.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,马爹利先生, 安迪还没用放行棋\N就走骑士了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Martell, Andy moved his knight\Nwithout doing the little hook thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:19:00.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不一定非要\N用放行棋. 那是随意的.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:19:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do\Nthe little hook thing. That's optional.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:06.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪, 走骑士\N必须先走放行棋.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, the knight\Nhas to do the little hook thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:09.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 每次都要吗?\N- 那是一种特权.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Every time?\N- lt's a privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:13.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,其它没有一个是这样走的.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one else gets to make that move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:16.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧, 马爹利先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Mr. Martell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:23.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜有些人才不会想那么多\N他们爱干啥干啥.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess some people don't know\Nquite as much as they think they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:27.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,将军.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:39.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们\N最好来见你.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought it best\Nwe come see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所知, 那个在我后颈\N的图案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, that pattern\Non the back of my neck
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:51.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是我遇到那个什么时\N出现的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,appeared during my experience\Nwith...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:54.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当然,\N不知道当时它怎么会在那儿的.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course,\Nno idea as to how it got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:56.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后你今天注意到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you noticed it today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:20:00.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的圆木注意到的. 我记得.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:20:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My log noticed. l remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:02.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你记得什么, 玛格利特?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you remember, Margaret?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:06.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的后腿.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the back of my leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:20.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我那时才7岁.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was 7 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:23.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时正走在树林子里,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l went walking up in the woods,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:29.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后当我回来时, 我被告知\N原来我已经失踪1天了.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when l got back, l was told\Nthat l had disappeared for a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:32.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我能记起的全部就是一道闪光,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All l could recall was a flash of light,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.47,0:20:36.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和我腿上的这印记.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that mark was on my leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:39.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们3个都记的那光.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all three recall the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:43.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有, 猫头鹰的叫声.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, the call of the owl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 我记得.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, l remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:52.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还仅有另一次\N我又见过那景象和听过那声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only other time l saw that sight\Nand heard that sound
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.47,0:20:55.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就在我丈夫去世前.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was right before my husband died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:58.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在火里.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:10.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我和某些事有着关联.\N- 是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l'm connecting with something.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:12.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:16.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:22.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}噢, 别把我埋葬{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, bury me not
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:27.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}在往昔的大草原上\N郊狼在那儿哀嚎{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the old prairie\NWhere the coyotes howl
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:31.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}风呼呼的吹{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the wind blows free
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:37.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}在一个狭窄的墓穴里,\N3个旁边躺着6个{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln a narrow grave,\NSix-by-3
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:40.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}不要现在埋葬我{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bury me now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:44.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}在孤单的大草原上{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the lone prairie
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:50.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,之前没人对我\N唱过歌.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's ever sung a song\Nto me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:54.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有人对你唱过小夜曲\N至少会有一次或两次.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have been serenaded\Nat least once or twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:58.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我没受到多少歌唱的启发.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't inspire much singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.99,0:22:02.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,大多数男孩都害怕.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.30,0:22:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most boys are afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.78,0:22:04.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 只是他们不了解你.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they don't know you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:08.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真不了解.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.56,0:22:11.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不觉得\N有任何人了解我.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't think\Nanybody really knows me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.95,0:22:16.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,听起来像是个警告.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt sounds like a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:18.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.34,0:22:21.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有另一个人...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf there's another guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:29.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,曾经有过一个,\N但不复存在了.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was someone,\Nbut not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:31.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不再有了.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:35.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 你现在打算怎么办呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you wanna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:40.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,知道牛仔的一些小把戏吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know anymore cowboy tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:44.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有一个套索\N在那个野餐篮子里,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.31,0:22:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you've got a lariat\Nin that picnic basket,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:45.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我能套住路过的家畜.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.61,0:22:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l could lasso passing cattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:49.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想这儿几里内都不会有一头奶牛的.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't think there's a cow for miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:52.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那就套迷路狗, 浣熊,\N鸟, 黄鼠狼.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.75,0:22:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stray dogs, raccoons,\Nbirds, weasels.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:21.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有人来看你.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.47,0:23:23.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.78,0:23:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:27.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个和你上医校的\N叫杰尔·奎格的人.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.48,0:23:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody you went to medical school\Nwith named Gerald Craig.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.08,0:23:32.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杰尔·奎格?\N那不可能, 唐娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gerald Craig?\NThat's not possible, Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.08,0:23:36.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 真的. 他说他去\N斯波坎市参加会议.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah. He said he was on his way\Nto a convention in Spokane.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:38.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他还知道我的一切.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He knew everything about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.82,0:23:48.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是他的号码, 还有这个.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's his number, and this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:56.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杰尔·奎格是我的室友.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.11,0:23:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gerald Craig was my roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.04,0:24:00.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,后来他在蛇河\N玩漂流艇时淹死了.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.32,0:24:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He drowned on a rafting trip\Non the Snake River.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:03.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时就在那儿, 唐娜.\N我还尝试去救他.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.55,0:24:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was there, Donna.\Nl tried to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.69,0:24:04.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 那...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:08.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是个公墓.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.53,0:24:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's a cemetery.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.17,0:24:19.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,骑士对王的主教，三.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.44,0:24:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knight to King's Bishop 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.86,0:24:25.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人, 他非常危险.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.14,0:24:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man, he's very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.60,0:24:27.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别再让他进来这儿,\N你听懂了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.91,0:24:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him in here again,\Ndo you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.77,0:24:31.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 肯定了.\N- 我拿这个去给库珀.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.05,0:24:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sure.\N- l've got to take this to Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.34,0:24:44.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,纳丁, 我在这\N要对你说的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.63,0:24:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nadine, what l'm here\Nto say to you is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.99,0:24:49.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看着你现在和迈克...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.30,0:24:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing how you're with Mike now...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.43,0:24:53.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看你窘的\N好可爱.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.74,0:24:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's so cute the way\Nyou get embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.73,0:24:58.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,既然\N我也已经有别人了...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.01,0:24:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And since\Nl have found someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.21,0:25:01.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,纳丁, 我不肯定\N你明不明白这事.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.51,0:25:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nadine, l'm not sure\Nyou're gonna understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.77,0:25:04.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当然, 我明白, 小艾艾.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.08,0:25:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, l understand, Eddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.60,0:25:07.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这又不是在耍嘴皮子.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.88,0:25:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't just a little spat.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.90,0:25:09.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,纳丁,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.19,0:25:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nadine,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.69,0:25:13.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道\N艾德正在提议什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.96,0:25:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you know\Nwhat Ed is suggesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.82,0:25:19.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不太明显.\N我们又不是, 就像, 在这儿探讨相对论.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.09,0:25:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not too obvious.\NWe're not, like, talking relativity here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.21,0:25:23.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在分手呢.\N主要来说, 是终结性分手.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.50,0:25:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're breaking up.\NMajor, final breakup.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.73,0:25:28.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 是啊, 从学术上来说,\N我想这算是一个分手, 但--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.04,0:25:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes, technically,\Nl guess it is a breakup, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.90,0:25:31.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 不过还不止\N是那样而已t, 纳丁.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.21,0:25:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a little more\Nthan that, Nadine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.86,0:25:35.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德, 你好严肃.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.14,0:25:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ed, you are so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.86,0:25:38.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在都什么年代了.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.15,0:25:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the dating years.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.56,0:25:42.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你表现的好像\N发生了什么大事.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.85,0:25:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting like\Nthis is some really big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.21,0:25:43.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,医生?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.49,0:25:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.77,0:25:49.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德, 这枚什么秘诀\N或咒语.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.06,0:25:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ed, there are no secret tricks\Nor magic words.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.90,0:25:55.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是伤口旁的\N疤痕组织逐渐消褪.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.20,0:25:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's like the dissolving\Nof scar tissue around a wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.30,0:26:00.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当她的脑袋开始感觉安全后\N她会再次重新认识现实.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.57,0:26:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll start to see reality again\Nwhen her mind begins to feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.17,0:26:03.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 将会是什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.47,0:26:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when will that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.51,0:26:05.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,难说.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.81,0:26:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.43,0:26:08.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那些组织包块堆积在那儿\N相当难搞.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.71,0:26:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tissue's packed in there\Npretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.21,0:26:13.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了. 这样, 1件事\N我实在不想看到的, 艾德,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.48,0:26:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Well, one thing\Nl really don't wanna see, Ed,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.21,0:26:18.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不要因嫉妒而愤怒.\N不要迈克因此发生任何意外.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.49,0:26:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are any incidents with Mike.\NNo jealous rages.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.08,0:26:22.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 要不只发生一件好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.36,0:26:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.08,0:26:25.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我放弃了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.36,0:26:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.47,0:26:34.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,纳丁, 你和艾德\N准备要离婚了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.77,0:26:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nadine, you and Ed\Nare about to get a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.12,0:26:42.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我的左眼已经瞎了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.41,0:26:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think l've gone blind in my left eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.86,0:27:37.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 雪莉?\N- 怎么.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.17,0:27:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Shelly?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.30,0:27:40.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看过这个了?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.60,0:27:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.77,0:27:43.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, "双峰小姐."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.07,0:27:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ''Miss Twin Peaks.''
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.34,0:27:48.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 你肯定是拿我来开玩笑.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.65,0:27:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you've gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.99,0:27:51.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有一个现金奖\N和一个奖学金.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.28,0:27:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a cash prize\Nand a scholarship.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.99,0:27:54.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我打赌你肯定能行.\N- 我不觉得.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.28,0:27:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l bet you could walk away with it.\N- l don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.82,0:27:57.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很容易的, 你来段演说,\N再问你几个问题...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.12,0:27:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's easy, you give a speech,\Nyou answer a few questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.38,0:28:05.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,双食店小姐, 你会做点什么\N为世界带来和平呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.69,0:28:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Double R Diner, what would\Nyou do to bring about world peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.29,0:28:09.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 我会把\N全世界的领袖聚在一起,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.60,0:28:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l would bring\Nall the world leaders together,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.99,0:28:13.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让他们围成一圈\N手拉手.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.27,0:28:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,make them form a circle\Nand join hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.29,0:28:16.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你握着拳头的话\N就不能手拉手咯.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.61,0:28:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you can't make a fist\Nholding hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.47,0:28:17.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你赢定了.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.78,0:28:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a shoo-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.16,0:28:20.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有一张单要下呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.44,0:28:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have an order up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.08,0:28:32.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你的汉堡来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.36,0:28:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your burger.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.82,0:28:35.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么高兴的要跳起舞来?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.09,0:28:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.21,0:28:39.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 我老板说我应该去\N参加选美. 双峰小姐.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.49,0:28:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my boss told me l should\Nenter a pageant. Miss Twin Peaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.08,0:28:44.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以当它是个玩笑,\N但你非常漂亮.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.37,0:28:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can kid about it,\Nbut you are very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.51,0:28:45.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你应该参选.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.80,0:28:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think you should enter it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.12,0:28:49.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢, 但我不觉得\N我自己有多漂亮.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.41,0:28:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, but l don't think\Nof myself as pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.16,0:28:51.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那时主观而已, 你知道的.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.47,0:28:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's an inner thing, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.25,0:29:08.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你要喝点什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.56,0:29:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.12,0:29:14.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的, 请给我来一杯\N浓黑咖啡.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.39,0:29:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, l'd like a cup\Nof deep black joe please.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.60,0:29:16.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,马上来.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.90,0:29:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.77,0:29:27.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是诺玛的妹妹.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.04,0:29:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Norma's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.34,0:29:28.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是安妮.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.65,0:29:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.16,0:29:32.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你怎么知道?\N- 戴尔·库珀. 地方执法机关.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.45,0:29:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- How did you know?\N- Dale Cooper. Local law enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.43,0:29:35.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一定很忙吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.72,0:29:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must keep you pretty busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.25,0:29:37.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,的确是.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.56,0:29:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.51,0:29:43.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你会在镇上呆一段时间?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.79,0:29:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you staying in town for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.08,0:29:45.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能会在这呆好长一阵子.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.36,0:29:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l might be here quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.73,0:29:47.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.03,0:29:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.43,0:29:49.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看来你挺喜欢这里的.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.70,0:29:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's grown on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.82,0:29:52.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里有它的魅力所在.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.10,0:29:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt has a way of doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.03,0:30:07.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我煮的有点浓.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.32,0:30:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l made it a little strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.34,0:30:09.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没事.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.62,0:30:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.29,0:30:24.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你煮的味道刚刚好, 安妮.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.57,0:30:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made it just right, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.95,0:30:43.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们书屋那边\N有麻烦了.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.22,0:30:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a problem\Nat the Book House.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.95,0:30:47.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀探员, 豪克,\N警长抓狂了.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.22,0:30:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper, Hawk,\Nthe sheriff's gone off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.29,0:30:49.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有钉子固定的家俱\N都给他打个稀巴烂.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.59,0:30:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's broken every piece\Nof furniture not nailed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.99,0:30:51.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我真不知该怎么办才好.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.30,0:30:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l honestly don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.03,0:30:54.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的, 安迪.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.33,0:30:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's okay, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.16,0:31:03.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿, 戴尔副警长.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.44,0:31:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Deputy Dale.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.69,0:31:05.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,工作如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.98,0:31:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's business?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.34,0:31:10.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 哈里,\N现在有一点点复杂了.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.65,0:31:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Harry,\Nit's a little complicated at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.47,0:31:15.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是法律的好处了,\N它没有生命, 你不能杀死它!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.75,0:31:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good thing about the law,\Nit doesn't breathe, you can't kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.03,0:31:25.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 我有一个想法.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.33,0:31:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, l've got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.77,0:31:28.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不把枪给我呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.07,0:31:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you hand me that gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.60,0:31:42.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信在我一生人中\N会把我的枪交到任何一个人手中!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.91,0:31:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't believe l've ever handed my gun\Nover to anybody in my entire life!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.95,0:31:47.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这或许\N就是个开始的好时机.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.22,0:31:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be\Na damn fine time to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.64,0:31:53.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道\N我做过的其他事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.92,0:31:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know something else\Nl've never done?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.55,0:31:59.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没横渡过海洋.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.83,0:31:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've never crossed the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.55,0:32:03.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,从未去过中国.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.87,0:32:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never got to China.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.42,0:32:09.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而她来到我身边.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.71,0:32:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.03,0:32:13.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她让所有事都变得美好起来.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.31,0:32:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she made everything better.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.90,0:32:18.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所有事都是那么美好.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.18,0:32:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything so much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.90,0:32:24.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.19,0:32:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.69,0:32:29.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你的生活仍属于你自己的.\N乔西并没有带着它一起走.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.96,0:32:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is still your own.\NJosie didn't take that with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.55,0:32:31.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我本应该带她走.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.86,0:32:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l should have gotten her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.77,0:32:34.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我早该\N带她离开这里!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.06,0:32:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l should have\Ntaken her away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.29,0:32:41.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱她.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.57,0:32:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.16,0:32:46.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她本不该死的.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.48,0:32:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't have to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.64,0:33:06.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.93,0:33:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.77,0:33:10.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有太多事情我不明白.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.07,0:33:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a whole lot l don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.99,0:33:15.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都那样.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.27,0:33:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.38,0:33:33.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚找人\N看着他.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.66,0:33:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have somebody keep an eye\Non him tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.51,0:33:35.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没见过他这样.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.79,0:33:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've never seen him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.03,0:33:38.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那就像你去\N最心爱的地方远足
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.33,0:33:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was like taking a hike\Nto your favorite spot
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.99,0:33:41.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,却发现曾在那儿的湖\N已经枯竭成空洞.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.26,0:33:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and finding a hole\Nwhere the lake used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.47,0:33:44.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西是有能量的.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.77,0:33:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie had power.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.21,0:33:49.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爱一个人不容易啊,\N付出太多.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.50,0:33:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who doesn't love easily,\Nloves too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.73,0:33:53.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 一个好人.\N- 最好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.01,0:33:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- A good man.\N- The best.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.12,0:33:56.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,继续前进.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.41,0:33:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.08,0:34:05.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你们定的特别蜜月套房\N庆门先生和夫人?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.35,0:34:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a special honeymoon suite\Nfor Mr. and Mrs. Hinkman?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.51,0:34:07.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对. 是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.79,0:34:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.82,0:34:09.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是从波斯曼州来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.13,0:34:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're from Bozeman originally.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.69,0:34:13.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我太太觉得\N看看郊野景色会不错.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.96,0:34:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my wife thought that it would be\Nnice to see the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.86,0:34:17.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有, 你知道吗, 你们双峰镇这儿\N的乡村非常漂亮.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.17,0:34:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, you know, you have some\Nvery pretty country here in Twin Peaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.86,0:34:20.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你会在我们这久住吗?\N- 就怕不够久.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.17,0:34:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Will you be with us long?\N- Not long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.38,0:34:26.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 住到明天就可以了,\N因为我们准备出深海钓鱼.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.67,0:34:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just until tomorrow if that's okay,\Nbecause we're going deep sea fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.64,0:34:28.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 太好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.95,0:34:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, goody.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.42,0:34:31.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好, 那我们现在\N准备上房去了, 我和--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.71,0:34:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so we'll just be\Ngoing on up now, me and--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.51,0:34:33.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我和庆门太太.\N- 噢, 是迈克吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.82,0:34:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Me and Mrs. Hinkman.\N- Oh, is that Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.42,0:34:40.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,苏珊, 你好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.72,0:34:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Susan, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.08,0:34:43.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.36,0:34:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.47,0:34:46.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,学校见.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.76,0:34:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll see you at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.21,0:34:53.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请上房吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.50,0:34:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The room please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.60,0:34:56.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,行李我们会自己拿的.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.87,0:34:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think we can handle the bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.21,0:35:03.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,首先,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.48,0:35:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.42,0:35:09.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想感谢你们在座的各位来\N出席这个不可思议的盛会.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.72,0:35:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l would like to thank all of you\Nfor this marvelous turnout.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.51,0:35:11.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴看到\N那么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.79,0:35:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's very gratifying to see\Nso many people
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.95,0:35:17.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真切的\N关心身处的环境.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.26,0:35:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who are sincere\Nabout their environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.95,0:35:23.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,『停止格斯伍』作战计划\N对那些企图
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.23,0:35:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Stop Ghostwood campaign\Nis a determined effort
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.73,0:35:27.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把我们美丽的西南森林\N变成畸怪大型游乐场
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.00,0:35:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to keep the rabid development\Ninterests from trying to turn
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.90,0:35:32.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,相关的急剧发展\N起到决定性的影响.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.21,0:35:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our beautiful Northwest forests\Ninto a monstrous amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.90,0:35:38.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,毁坏几个世纪以来\N未被骚扰过的动物保护区.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.21,0:35:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroying animal preserves which\Nhave been undisturbed for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.47,0:35:41.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个小小的世界\N是几种濒临灭绝动物
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.75,0:35:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The little worlds\Nthat serve as sanctums
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.08,0:35:45.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,的栖息圣地.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.39,0:35:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for several endangered species.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.68,0:35:51.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是\N小松鼬.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.96,0:35:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not the least of which\Nis the little pine-weasel.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.25,0:35:55.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，在这结束之前,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.53,0:35:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before moving along,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.86,0:36:03.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想再次提醒大家\N生态学不是一种奢侈科学.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.14,0:36:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l would just like to remind all of us\Nthat ecology is not a luxury science.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.51,0:36:06.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它也不是一场\N取悦大家的秀.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.81,0:36:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt is not about\Npleasant appearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.95,0:36:10.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而是关乎生存.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.25,0:36:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt is about survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.99,0:36:18.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,关乎我们是否做好\N长期进行下去的准备.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.28,0:36:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About whether we are all\Ngoing to make it, period.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.77,0:36:25.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但千万不要低估了\N视觉享受的价值,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.06,0:36:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not to understate the value\Nof visual pleasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.08,0:36:30.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们马上来到时装表演环节.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.36,0:36:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we come to the fashion show.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.47,0:36:35.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 如果你们当中任何人觉得\N有些模特很眼熟,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.77,0:36:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if any of you think you recognize\Nsome of the models,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.81,0:36:38.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为他们\N就是来自本地社区的居民,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.11,0:36:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's because they are concerned\Nmembers of the community,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.16,0:36:41.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚慷慨仁慈的贡献出\N他们宝贵的时间.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.44,0:36:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who have graciously given\Nof their time tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.68,0:36:45.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 女士们，先生们,\N闲话少说, 这是我们的主持人,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.98,0:36:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, ladies and gentlemen,\Nto kick things off, here is our host,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.51,0:36:47.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,理查·揣眉.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.82,0:36:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard Tremayne.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.68,0:36:55.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你. 济济一堂啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.99,0:36:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Splendid gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.16,0:36:59.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的小露西\N正穿这一套令人愉悦的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.46,0:37:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our little Lucy\Nis wearing a delightful
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.99,0:37:04.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,合成针织保暖装, 既有北方的舒适感\N又有南方的潇洒自如.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.30,0:37:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mix of warm, northern comfort\Nand southern insouciance.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.86,0:37:10.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一件优雅的精纺羊绒外套\N外加一条彩格披肩,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.17,0:37:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An elegant worsted wool jacket\Nover a plethora of plaid,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.34,0:37:13.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再以波尔卡小圆点衬衫作点缀.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.61,0:37:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a hint of polka dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.77,0:37:18.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,实在无与伦比, 是吧?\N在一个漆黑的无月之夜, 穿上修身短裙
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.05,0:37:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's fabulous, isn't it?\NA moonless night, black, slim skirt
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.34,0:37:23.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那身打扮就似乎在向世界说,\N"嘿, 我在这儿呢."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.62,0:37:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a look that always says,\N''Hey, world, l'm here.''
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.12,0:37:39.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,布伦南先生现在身上正穿着的是\N一件消防车风格的红色高领毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.43,0:37:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Brennan is wearing\Na fire engine red turtleneck
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.38,0:37:42.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在全羊毛彩格披肩衬托下的是\N潘多腾衬衫.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.67,0:37:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,beneath an all-wool plaid\NPendleton shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.12,0:37:48.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,水牛纹短马靴令他更显\N红黑相间的整体感.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.41,0:37:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He completes this look with his red\Nand black, buffalo-checked jodhpurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.29,0:37:50.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,犹如一份宣言\N为男人保留着
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.58,0:37:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the man who wants\Nto make a statement
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.55,0:37:56.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,想要的随意感,\N无论他是在外工作的征途中,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.85,0:37:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while retaining that casual feel,\Nwhether he's out mastering a task,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.25,0:38:00.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还是乘着仆仆风尘\N去赴会.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.52,0:38:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or riding the breeze\Nof a chance meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.12,0:38:03.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了, 安迪.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.39,0:38:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.42,0:38:14.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,照这样下去, 我们都要迟了.\N所以，等下我们出去那
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.70,0:38:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we're running late.\NSo if we could all sort
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.07,0:38:17.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,动作要快点\N全都快快跟着理查.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.37,0:38:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of hurry Richard along\Nwith some quick movement out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.99,0:38:18.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我穿这着这东西好热.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.28,0:38:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm hot in this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.21,0:38:23.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你热? 我还穿的像只绵羊呢.\N这全都是精纺厚绒呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.48,0:38:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hot? l'm dressed like a sheep.\NAll this worsted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.99,0:38:25.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我想揣眉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.28,0:38:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l think Mr. Tremayne
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.51,0:38:28.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看到这些女孩子\N会更热呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.78,0:38:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is getting more than a little hot\Nwith all these girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.34,0:38:31.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们的下一位模特是...\N- 去, 去, 去.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.62,0:38:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Our next model...\N- Go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.42,0:38:36.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊, 这不就是环保领袖约翰·缪尔吗?\N红杉树之友啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.73,0:38:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it isn't John Muir,\Nfriend of the redwoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.16,0:38:40.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳, 你来真好.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.46,0:38:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine, how good of you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.60,0:38:44.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本, 亲爱的,\N你这忽悠的都什么人啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.90,0:38:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, darling,\Nwho are you kidding with all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.29,0:38:48.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对是百分之一百的诚心诚意.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.60,0:38:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am absolutely 1 00 percent sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.16,0:38:52.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 少来了吧.\N看你在跟谁说话.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.47,0:38:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.\NLook who you're talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.12,0:38:55.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都一条道上的.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.41,0:38:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same line of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.16,0:39:01.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你一向都\N有点显而易见的, 除了这次.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.45,0:39:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been\Na little more obvious, but this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.81,0:39:06.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳, 在你的一生里,\N曾有过,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.09,0:39:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine, have you ever,\Nin your entire life,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.47,0:39:09.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真正改变你的\N体验吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.76,0:39:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had an experience\Nthat truly changed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.99,0:39:14.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了, 省着点吧，想重新兜揽生意的话\N就老实对我说好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.29,0:39:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, spare me the born-again\Nsales pitch and level with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.29,0:39:16.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你别指望阻挡\N我的发展大计,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.60,0:39:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hope to stop\Nmy development plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.99,0:39:19.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,说, 你到底期望\N在这事上能获得些什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.30,0:39:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so, what do you actually expect\Nto gain from all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.90,0:39:23.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次荡涤
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.17,0:39:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A first scrubbing
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.03,0:39:29.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那一颗整个西北\N最肮脏的良心.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.31,0:39:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on one of the dirtiest consciences\Nin the entire Northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.21,0:39:33.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我满怀希望, 它也会在你身上发生的.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.51,0:39:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And hopefully, it will happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.21,0:39:35.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.52,0:39:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.55,0:39:40.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你格斯伍的\N计划是什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.86,0:39:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know what your plans\Nfor Ghostwood are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.16,0:39:45.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我以前看待人生的方式\N的确和你一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.46,0:39:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And granted l used to see life\Nexactly the way you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.38,0:39:51.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且不管我做了多少生意\N赚了多少钱,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.66,0:39:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And no matter how many deals\Nl made or how much money l made,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.47,0:39:57.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在内里, 我仍是一个漆黑,\N悲哀，泥头泥脸的土佬而已.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.77,0:39:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,inside, l was still a black,\Nmiserable clod of dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.34,0:40:02.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而我现在寻找的是一件\N在生命真正让你快乐的事,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.64,0:40:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am finding that the one thing\Nthat really affords you joy in life,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.90,0:40:07.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一靠得住的事, 就是施与.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.18,0:40:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the only authentic thing, is giving.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.03,0:40:12.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不要等到你临死的那一天\N才发现这个真理.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.32,0:40:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wait until you're on\Nyour deathbed to find that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.86,0:40:15.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝保佑你!.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.16,0:40:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.03,0:40:18.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,给你说的好像是那么回事儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.33,0:40:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually sound like you mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.55,0:40:26.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的. 为了你, 为了我, 未来.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.86,0:40:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l do. For you, for me, the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.03,0:40:33.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳,\N为什么你不借这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.34,0:40:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine,\Nwhy don't you take this opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.51,0:40:38.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去超越你的自大狂\N和一生的自私自利,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.81,0:40:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to transcend a lifetime\Nof megalomania and egocentricity,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.07,0:40:44.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后给我们写张巨额支票\N作为停止格斯伍计划的活动经费.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.38,0:40:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and write us a big fat check\Nto help stop Ghostwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.90,0:41:03.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那现在, 为你们介绍的是\N一只濒临绝种的小生物,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.21,0:41:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, to introduce you\Nto an endangered little critter,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.81,0:41:05.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它的家园\N最近正遭受着
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.11,0:41:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whose home\Nis presently under attack
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.64,0:41:10.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,被提上议程的格斯伍发展计划\N的无情糟蹋, 有请提姆·品寇先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.94,0:41:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the proposed Ghostwood\Ndevelopment project, Mr. Tim Pinkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.21,0:41:16.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你, 基巴.\N谢谢你, 谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.48,0:41:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Dick.\NThank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.68,0:41:22.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好, 嗨, 一切都还好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.99,0:41:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hi, how's everything going?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.42,0:41:29.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.73,0:41:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.60,0:41:33.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,女士们，先生们,\N我带来了一个小伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.90,0:41:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,\Nl have with me a little fellow
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.73,0:41:38.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它不知道\N危险在等着他.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.01,0:41:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who doesn't understand\Nthe peril that awaits him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.64,0:41:42.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个天真无知在一个发疯似的世界里.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.94,0:41:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An innocent in a world gone mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.86,0:41:46.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个发疯似的世界.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.15,0:41:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world gone mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.64,0:41:50.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不再囉嗦了,\N女士们，先生们,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.95,0:41:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without further ado,\Nladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.29,0:42:00.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你们呈现\N濒临绝种的松鼬.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.59,0:42:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l give you\Nthe endangered pine-weasel.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.34,0:42:04.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在看到的这个是\N鼬鼠家族的其中一个品种.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.63,0:42:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this species\Nis of the weasel family.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.81,0:42:12.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他不单止对我们人类\N没有任何侵犯性，而且还有美丽的皮毛,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.10,0:42:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And not only is he non-aggressive\Nto us humans and has beautiful fur,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.25,0:42:18.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,并且, 他天生就是\N啮齿类中控制能力的佼佼者.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.54,0:42:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but also, he is by nature\Nan excellent controller of rodents.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.33,0:42:23.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不幸的是, 这友善的小家伙\N有难以置信的好奇心
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.65,0:42:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, this little friendly fellow\Nis incredibly curious
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.34,0:42:26.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这让他很容易\N中圈套.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.62,0:42:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,making him very easy\Nfor one to trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.07,0:42:31.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他还会被明亮发光的物体\N所吸引.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.36,0:42:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is also attracted to bright\Nshiny objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.42,0:42:34.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 一定是给我的胸章吸引了.\N- 对啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.73,0:42:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Must be my studs.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.38,0:42:38.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一样令人吃惊的,\N信不信由你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.67,0:42:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt also is amazing,\Nhe is particularly attracted
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.68,0:42:42.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他还特别容易被多种气味所吸引,\N尤其那种非常廉价的古龙水.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.97,0:42:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to various smells like, believe it or not,\Nvery cheap cologne.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.64,0:42:44.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 这是干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.94,0:42:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.73,0:42:46.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想它要\N给你一个吻, 基巴.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.01,0:42:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think it wants\Nto give you a kiss, Dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.90,0:42:50.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 噢, 别了, 品寇先生.\N- 来嘛. 来嘛.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.18,0:42:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, please, Mr. Pinkle.\N- Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.07,0:42:56.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好啦, 给他一个吻嘛.\N- 一个吻?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.38,0:42:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- lt's all right, give him a kiss.\N- A kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.25,0:42:58.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好样的. 来一个.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.55,0:42:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attaboy. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.86,0:43:01.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好, 看这儿, 小香客--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.16,0:43:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, there, little pilgrim--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.25,0:43:06.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 不, 不, 不.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.56,0:43:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.29,0:43:17.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,大家别慌张. 别慌张.\N他是完全无害的.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.57,0:43:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody panic. Don't panic.\NHe's completely harmless.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.29,0:43:18.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他已经快濒临绝种了.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.58,0:43:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already endangered.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.20,0:43:34.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别慌张, 各位,\N请别慌张.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.49,0:43:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic, anybody,\Njust don't panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.60,0:43:36.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 大家别慌张.\N- 请各位, 冷静.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.89,0:43:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Nobody panic.\N- Please everyone, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.12,0:43:39.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,留在你的座位.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.40,0:43:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay in your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.25,0:43:43.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你还好吧?\N- 我还好.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.53,0:43:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You all right?\N- l'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.20,0:43:46.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一只开溜鼬鼠引发的骚动.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.50,0:43:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lot of fuss over a loose weasel.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.25,0:43:48.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 或许我们该帮忙.\N- 我不知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.54,0:43:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Maybe we should help.\N- l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.77,0:43:51.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有点小刺激\N对这帮人可能是好事.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.07,0:43:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little excitement\Nmight do this crowd some good.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.60,0:43:56.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你来看时装表演吗?\N- 不, 我来看你.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.88,0:43:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Did you come for the fashion show?\N- No, l came for you.
